# Revisions that only moved whitespace. `git blame --ignore-revs-file` skips
# them so blame keeps pointing at the commit that wrote the line's *meaning*.
#
# Configure it once per checkout:
#   git config blame.ignoreRevsFile .git-blame-ignore-revs
#
# GitHub applies this file automatically in its blame view.

